This paper involves the use of convolutional neural networks for image processing and decision making, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also deals with autonomous exploration and surveillance, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The use of deep learning for decision making and optimization also falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with the reconstruction of 3D environments, which falls under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
